%p
  Hi #{@ticket_request.user.first_name},
%p
  This is a confirmation that we have received your ticket request for
  = @event.name

%p
  You'll receive a follow-up email when your request has been approved, at
  which point you'll be able purchase your tickets and sign up for volunteer
  shifts at the event.

%p
  You can also view the
  = link_to 'status of your request',
    event_ticket_request_url(@event, @ticket_request)
  at any time.

%p
  Thanks,
  %br
  The #{@event.name} team
